show.description: A powerful CEO’s pregnant wife finds herself trapped in a web of jealousy, betrayal, and cruelty at the hands of a scheming secretary. With her dignity torn apart and her safety at stake, she refuses to bow down. This is the story of a woman’s unbreakable fight for truth, justice, and her rightful place.
